@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how the Cinema App ("the Application") collects, uses,
    stores, and protects personal data provided by its users.
</p>

<h2>Personal Data We Collect</h2>
<p>
    The Application may collect and process the following types of personal data:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Account information such as username and email address</li>
    <li>Authentication and authorization data required for user login</li>
    <li>Application-related data associated with movie browsing, screenings, and reservations</li>
</ul>

<h2>Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
<p>
    Personal data is collected and processed solely for the purposes of:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Providing access to the Application and its features</li>
    <li>Managing user accounts and authentication</li>
    <li>Ensuring proper functionality and improving the user experience</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>
    All personal data is stored in a secure database environment.
    Appropriate technical and organizational measures are implemented to protect data
    against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.
</p>

<h2>Cookies and Session Data</h2>
<p>
    The Application uses cookies and session-based technologies strictly for authentication
    and security purposes. These are essential for the correct operation of the Application.
</p>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
<p>
    The Application does not share, sell, or transfer personal data to third parties.
    This project is developed for educational and demonstration purposes.
</p>

<h2>User Rights</h2>
<p>
    Users have the right to access, update, or request deletion of their personal data
    through their account settings or by contacting the Application administrator.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>
    This Privacy Policy may be updated to reflect changes in the Application or applicable
    requirements. Any updates will be published on this page.
</p>

<h2>Contact Information</h2>
<p>
    For questions or concerns related to this Privacy Policy, please contact the Application administrator.
</p>
